<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS via CDN with Forms plugin -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts: Inter -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google Material Icons -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
        }
        .error-bg {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgb(180, 30, 30) 0%, rgb(45, 10, 10) 90.1%);
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    borderRadius: {
                        'DEFAULT': '0.5rem',
                        'lg': '1rem'
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="error-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <!-- Glow spheres -->
    <div class="absolute w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-red-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] top-10 left-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-orange-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] bottom-10 right-10 pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="w-full max-w-2xl bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/20 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl relative z-10 my-8">
        <!-- Logo and header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500/30 rounded-2xl text-red-300 mb-4 shadow-inner">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[40px]" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">database_off</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-[22px] font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Koneksi Database Gagal</h2>
            <p class="text-[12px] text-red-200/70 mt-1 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Sistem Akuntansi Bengkel Presisi</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical Error Panel -->
        <div class="mb-8 bg-black/30 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/10 pb-2 mb-3">
                <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-red-300 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-1.5">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">error</span> Detail Kesalahan (MySQL Error)
                </span>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono">STATUS: 500</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[13px] text-red-200 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap break-all leading-relaxed"><%= error %></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Troubleshooting Steps -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-yellow-400">help</span> Panduan Solusi Mandiri:
            </h3>

            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-yellow-400/20 text-yellow-300 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[14px] shrink-0">1</div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-white">Periksa Status Layanan Aiven Anda</h4>
                    <p class="text-[12px] text-white/70 mt-1">
                        Database MySQL gratis dari **Aiven.io** otomatis di-pause jika tidak aktif selama beberapa hari. 
                        Buka akun Anda di <a href="https://aiven.io" target="_blank" class="text-sky-300 hover:underline">Aiven Console</a> dan pastikan status service Anda **RUNNING** (berwarna hijau). Jika statusnya *Paused*, klik tombol **Resume/Start** untuk mengaktifkannya kembali.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-yellow-400/20 text-yellow-300 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[14px] shrink-0">2</div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-white">Verifikasi Environment Variables di Vercel</h4>
                    <p class="text-[12px] text-white/70 mt-1">
                        Masuk ke dasbor **Vercel -> Project Settings -> Environment Variables**, dan pastikan kelima variabel di bawah ini sudah ditambahkan dengan benar (tanpa tanda kutip):
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto">
                        <table class="w-full text-left text-[11px] font-mono text-white/80 border-collapse border border-white/10">
                            <thead>
                                <tr class="bg-white/10">
                                    <th class="p-1.5 border border-white/10">Key</th>
                                    <th class="p-1.5 border border-white/10">Nilai Saat Ini</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 font-bold text-sky-300">DB_HOST</td>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 break-all"><%= host %></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 font-bold text-sky-300">DB_USER</td>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10"><%= user %></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 font-bold text-sky-300">DB_PORT</td>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10"><%= port %></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 font-bold text-sky-300">DB_NAME</td>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10"><%= database %></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 font-bold text-sky-300">DB_PASSWORD</td>
                                    <td class="p-1.5 border border-white/10 text-white/40">•••••••• (Disembunyikan)</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-4 rounded-xl">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-yellow-400/20 text-yellow-300 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-[14px] shrink-0">3</div>
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-white">Lakukan "Redeploy" di Vercel</h4>
                    <p class="text-[12px] text-white/70 mt-1">
                        Jika Anda melakukan perubahan Environment Variables, perubahan tersebut **hanya aktif setelah deployment baru**.
                        Buka tab **Deployments** di Vercel, klik tombol **tiga titik (`...`)** di sebelah kanan deployment terbaru Anda, lalu klik **Redeploy**.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Reload Button -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <button onclick="window.location.reload()" 
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-red-900 font-bold text-[13px] px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-slate-100 hover:scale-[1.01] transition-all">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">refresh</span> Hubungkan Ulang Sekarang
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
